Index starts at 0

>>> my_string[3] >>> my_string[4:9]

String Methods

>>> my_string.upper()

String to uppercase

>>> my_string.lower() >>> my_string.count('w')

String to lowercase Count String elements

>>> my_string.replace('e', 'i') Replace String elements

>>> my_string.strip()

Strip whitespaces

